[2026-03-11] SESSION 1 — Initial Data Exploration
──────────────────────────────────────────────────

## Dataset Overview
- File: data8514_SI/data8514_SI.dta
- Observations: 579,533 firm-year obs
- Variables: 98
- Year range: 1985–2014 (energy vars mostly 1990–2014)
- Unit identifier: psid (plant ID)

## Energy Variable Inventory

### Electricity
| Variable  | Description                        | Coverage     | Units     |
|-----------|------------------------------------|--------------|-----------|
| efuvcu    | Electricity expenditure (total)    | ~100% (3 NA) | Rp000     |

NOTE: efuvcu is NOT a sum of the fuel vcu vars — very low correlation (0.40
in 2005), and efuvcu is systematically smaller. It is a separate electricity
variable, available nearly complete across all years.

### Fuel Variables (zp* = production use, zn* = non-production use)
| Code | Energy Type (best guess, IBS convention) | Coverage     | Year Range |
|------|------------------------------------------|--------------|------------|
| zpdvcu / zndvcu | Solar/HSD (diesel)            | ~515K / 89%  | 1990–2014  |
| zpsvcu / znsvcu | Minyak tanah (kerosene)       | ~515K / 89%  | 1990–2014  |
| zpovcu / znovcu | Bensin/premium (gasoline)     | ~160K / 46%  | 1990–2014  |
| zpivcu / znivcu | Batubara (coal) or ind. fuel  | ~212K / 59%  | 1990–2014  |
| zpzvcu / znzvcu | Gas/LPG                       | ~172K / 30%  | 2001–2009  |
| zpxvcu / znxvcu | Other/electricity (PLN?)      | ~43K  / 7%   | 2005–2009  |

### Variable Structure
- `vcu` suffix = value in current Rupiah (Rp thousands assumed)
- `ccu` suffix = cost version (similar to vcu, purpose unclear — may be same thing)
- `kcu` suffix = physical quantity — VERY SPARSE (see below)

